#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_odps_table.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.read\\_odps\\_table"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:1 of
msgid "Read data from a MaxCompute (ODPS) table into DataFrame."
msgstr "从 MaxCompute (ODPS) 表中读取数据到 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:3 of
msgid ""
"Supports specifying some columns as indexes. If not specified, RangeIndex"
" will be generated."
msgstr "支持将某些列指定为索引。如果未指定，将生成 RangeIndex。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_odps_table.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:6 of
msgid "Name of the table to read from."
msgstr "要读取的表名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:8 of
msgid "Table partition or list of partitions to read from."
msgstr "要读取的表分区或分区列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:10 of
msgid ""
"Table columns to read from. You may also specify partition columns here. "
"If not specified, all table columns (or include partition columns if "
"`append_partitions` is True) will be included."
msgstr ""
"要读取的表列。您也可以在此处指定分区列。如果未指定，将包含所有表列（或者"
"如果 `append_partitions` 为 True，则包含分区列）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:14 of
msgid "Columns to be specified as indexes."
msgstr "指定为索引的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:16 of
msgid ""
"If True, will add all partition columns as selected columns when "
"`columns` is not specified,"
msgstr "如果为 True，当未指定 `columns` 时，将添加所有分区列作为选定列，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:19 of
msgid ""
"Back-end data type applied to the resultant DataFrame (still "
"experimental)."
msgstr "应用于结果 DataFrame 的后端数据类型（仍处于实验阶段）。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_odps_table.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:22 of
msgid "**result** -- DataFrame read from MaxCompute (ODPS) table"
msgstr "**result** -- 从 MaxCompute (ODPS) 表中读取的 DataFrame"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_odps_table.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

